v1.0.4 changes:
  - StockfishNative.java (EXPANDED, GPL v3): new @JavascriptInterface
      methods setChess960Mode(boolean) and isChess960Mode(). New
      private volatile field _pendingChess960 caches the current mode
      and is re-applied to the engine (via sendSetOptionAndWait) inside
      startEngine() after applySettings() on every (auto-)restart, so
      crash recovery does not silently drop UCI_Chess960=true. New
      Chess960-specific block in startEngine() (Step 6.5) handles this.
      ENGINE_VERSION constant updated to "v1.0.4".
  - ChessApp.java: Log message updated to "(v1.0.4)".
  - MainActivity.java: VERSION constant updated to "v1.0.4".
  - AndroidManifest.xml: versionCode 103 → 104, versionName "1.0.3" → "1.0.4".

